{"id":2929,"date":"2020-02-12T10:10:04","date_gmt":"2020-02-12T03:10:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/?p=2929"},"modified":"2020-02-12T11:25:40","modified_gmt":"2020-02-12T04:25:40","slug":"kinh-nghiem-chon-mua-rem-cua-dep-theo-xu-huong-2020","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/kinh-nghiem-chon-mua-rem-cua-dep-theo-xu-huong-2020.html","title":{"rendered":"Kinh Nghi\u1ec7m Ch\u1ecdn Mua R\u00e8m C\u1eeda \u0110\u1eb9p Theo Xu H\u01b0\u1edbng 2020"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong><em>R\u00e8m c\u1eeda b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong b\u1ea5t k\u00ec kh\u00f4ng gian n\u00e0o, n\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap t\u0103ng v\u1ebb sang tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n che ch\u1eafn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m c\u1eeda \u0111\u1eb9p, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t h\u00e0i h\u00f2a \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e3y theo d\u00f5i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam kinh nghi\u1ec7m khi l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m \u01b0ng \u00fd nh\u1ea5t.<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 130%; color: #000080;\"><strong>Ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u<\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">Trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ecdn l\u1ef1a ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u r\u00e8m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p gi\u00fap cho c\u0103n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n th\u00eam ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u1eebng phong c\u00e1ch ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1ec5. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a chu\u1ed9ng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-vai-mot-mau\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i<\/span><\/a>. Lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng t\u1ed1t, c\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t ch\u1ed1ng b\u1ee5i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, hay ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2930 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-vai-rem-vai-cao-cap-436x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1337\" height=\"1226\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-vai-rem-vai-cao-cap-436x400.jpg 436w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-vai-rem-vai-cao-cap-510x468.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-vai-rem-vai-cao-cap.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1337px) 100vw, 1337px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i &#8211; m\u1eabu r\u00e8m hot nh\u1ea5t 2020<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i pha m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat c\u1ed5 k\u00ednh th\u00ec l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-sao-go\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">r\u00e8m g\u1ed7<\/span><\/a> l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t. V\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m t\u1eeb g\u1ed7 t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean n\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-sao-go\/\">r\u00e8m s\u00e1o g\u1ed7<\/a><\/span> kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m c\u1eeda kh\u00e1c<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-sao-go\/\"> R\u00e8m s\u00e1o g\u1ed7<\/a><\/span> kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd b\u1ecb cong v\u00eanh, m\u1ed1i m\u1ecdt, v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ed1t. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-sao-go\/\">r\u00e8m s\u00e1o g\u1ed7<\/a><\/span> c\u00f2n c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t , gi\u00fap c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu, m\u00e1t m\u1ebb v\u1ea3o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u00e0 \u1ea5m \u00e1p v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2931 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-go-sang-trong-500x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1330\" height=\"1064\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-go-sang-trong-500x400.jpg 500w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-go-sang-trong-510x408.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-go-sang-trong-768x614.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-go-sang-trong-1000x800.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-sao-go-sang-trong.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1330px) 100vw, 1330px\" title=\"\"><em><strong>R\u00e8m s\u00e1o g\u1ed7 sang tr\u1ecdng, ti\u1ec7n \u00edch th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi con ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 130%;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080;\">Ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf r\u00e8m c\u1eeda<\/span><br \/>\n<\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3u thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf r\u00e8m c\u1eeda c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0i h\u00f2a v\u00e0 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n nh\u1ea5t. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n th\u00ec n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m c\u1eeda sang tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-cau-vong\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng<\/span><\/a> \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh s\u1ef1 nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng. H\u01a1n th\u1ebf n\u1eefa <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-cau-vong\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">R\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng<\/span><\/a> l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m c\u1eeda tinh t\u1ebf, s\u1ef1 \u0111an sen gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i s\u00e1ng t\u1ed1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e9o l\u00ean, h\u1ea1 xu\u1ed1ng g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ec7n d\u1ee5ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2932 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cau-vong-470x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1322\" height=\"1125\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cau-vong-470x400.jpg 470w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cau-vong-510x434.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cau-vong.jpg 512w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1322px) 100vw, 1322px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>r\u00e8m c\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi kh\u00f4ng gian<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">N\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111ang thi\u1ebft th\u1ebf theo phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i Ch\u00e2u \u00c2U th\u00ec n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-hai-lop\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i hai l\u1edbp<\/span><\/a> s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u0103ng th\u00eam s\u1ef1 sang tr\u1ecdng, quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n tinh t\u1ebf, d\u1ecbu d\u00e0ng. B\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn gam m\u00e0u r\u00e8m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t trong c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng, kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn gam m\u00e0u qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1i, s\u1ebd l\u00e0m c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean k\u00e9m s\u00e1ng, \u00e2m u. N\u00ean ch\u1ecdn gam m\u00e0u n\u00e2u, Ghi,&#8230; m\u00e0u s\u1eafc hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng lo l\u1ed7i mode<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2841 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/rem-tan-co-dien-075-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1327\" height=\"996\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/rem-tan-co-dien-075-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/rem-tan-co-dien-075-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/rem-tan-co-dien-075-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/rem-tan-co-dien-075-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/rem-tan-co-dien-075.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1327px) 100vw, 1327px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i 2 l\u1edbp sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch s\u1ef1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf phong c\u00e1ch Ch\u00e2u \u00e2u<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00f2ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf c\u00e1c t\u00f2a nh\u00e0 cao t\u1ea7ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u1eeda k\u00ednh, c\u00f3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 r\u00e8m c\u1eeda. V\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-cuon\/\">r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n<\/a><\/span> ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng d\u00e3i cho c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng, nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng, qu\u00e1n cafe. \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, s\u1ef1 d\u1ee5ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng gian<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2920 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-tron-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1360\" height=\"1020\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-tron-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-tron-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cuon-tron.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1360px) 100vw, 1360px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>r\u00e8m cu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi kh\u00f4ng gian<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 130%; color: #000080;\"><strong>Ch\u1ecdn m\u00e0u s\u1eafc<\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><strong><em>Ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m c\u1eeda c\u00f9ng t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u v\u1edbi m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u1eddng<\/em><\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">C\u00e1ch ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p r\u00e8m c\u1eeda v\u00e0 s\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng m\u00e0u ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u nh\u1ea5t trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1eafng hay kem th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m c\u1eeda c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0u s\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 mnag l\u1ea1i cho kh\u00f4ng gian nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 nh\u1ea5t qu\u00e1n t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 trong trang tr\u00ed n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2936 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cua-mau-kem-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1330\" height=\"1330\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cua-mau-kem-400x400.jpg 400w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cua-mau-kem-510x510.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cua-mau-kem-280x280.jpg 280w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cua-mau-kem-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cua-mau-kem.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1330px) 100vw, 1330px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>r\u00e8m c\u1eeda m\u00e0u kem c\u00f9ng m\u00e0u s\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><strong><em>R\u00e8m c\u1eeda v\u00e0 s\u01a1n t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc b\u1ed5 sung\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc b\u1ed5 sung d\u00f4i khi l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t cho kh\u00f4ng gian, v\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n nhau trong b\u00e1nh xe m\u00e0u. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00e1ch ph\u1ed1i m\u00e0u theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f4i khi h\u01a1i c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n l\u1ea1i l\u1edbn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a b\u1ed5 sung cho m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u1eddng<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2937 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cua-doi-mau-tuong-670x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1315\" height=\"785\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cua-doi-mau-tuong-670x400.jpg 670w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cua-doi-mau-tuong-510x304.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cua-doi-mau-tuong-768x458.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-cua-doi-mau-tuong.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1315px) 100vw, 1315px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>R\u00e8m c\u1eeda v\u00e0 m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u00e0i h\u00f2a b\u1ed5 sung cho nhau\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><em><strong>T\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian trung h\u00f2a<\/strong>\u00a0<\/em><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-size: 95%;\">R\u00e8m c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc trung t\u00ednh s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u00ean t\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ecbu h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 r\u00e8m c\u00f3 t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho nh\u1eefng b\u01b0c t\u01b0\u1eddng theo t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 l\u1ea1nh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f4ng gian d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 h\u01a1n, n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m c\u1eeda m\u00e0u ken, b\u01a1 cho nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0u \u1ea5m v\u00e0 r\u00e8m m\u00e0u x\u00e1m cho nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00e0u s\u01a1n l\u1ea1nh. B\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn r\u00e8m \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0u \u0111\u1ec3 mang l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng gian phong c\u00e1ch trung t\u00ednh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2938 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-mau-trung-tinh-355x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1372\" height=\"1546\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/rem-mau-trung-tinh-355x400.jpg 355